      <h2>Why Maquette</h2>
      <p>
        Maquette is a virtual DOM implementation that excels in both speed and simplicity.
        It solves the problem of keeping the user interface in sync with underlying data.
      </p>
      <p>
        Maquette allows you to specify the UI using plain Javascript.
        This makes maquette easy to learn, easy to debug and easy to deploy.
        Maquette is very unopionated by design,
        making integration with other frameworks and libraries as painless as possible.
      </p>
